'''Nikolai Aleksandrovich Abramov''' ({{lang-ru|<U+041D><U+0438><U+043A><U+043E><U+043B><U+0430><U+0439> <U+0410><U+043B><U+0435><U+043A><U+0441><U+0430><U+043D><U+0434><U+0440><U+043E><U+0432><U+0438><U+0447> <U+0410><U+0431><U+0440><U+0430><U+043C><U+043E><U+0432>}}; born January 5, 1984) is a [[Russia]]n professional [[Association football|football]] player. As of August 2009, he plays in the [[Russian Second Division]] for [[FC Ryazan]].

